Really bizarre event. One thing that I really enjoy about the new events added/changed for downfall is that the majority of them feel pretty good, and give you some strong options to make them worth a whole floor. This event basically never feels like it's worth a floor, the costs are incredibly high for what you're getting (just completely random colorless cards). I feel like at the very least you should be able to choose from 3 options, like on sensory stone. I have done the 30 gold option a few times just to see what happens, but the odds of getting something worth taking are against you. Spending 70 or 110 is basically never correct, unless you have singing bowl.

Overall, I believe that either the costs need to be drastically reduced, or you need to be able to choose from 3 options, like a normal card reward. Seeing 1 completely random card feels terrible
